<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/public/js/findPw.js" defer></script>
    <title>비밀번호 찾기</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/header.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/findPw.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header class="main-header">
        <div class="header-layout">
            <span class="header-logo logo"><a href="/">Chatta</a></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <p>가입 시 기재한 아이디와 이름을 입력해주세요</p>
    <form name="findPw-form">
        <div class="id">
            <label for="id">아이디</label>
            <input type="text" id="id" /><br />
        </div>
        <div class="name">
            <label for="name">이름</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" /><br />
        </div>
        <div class="btn">
            <div class="findPw_btn">
                <button type="button" onclick="findPw()">찾기</button>
            </div>
            <div class="cancel_btn">
                <button type="button" onclick="cancel()">취소</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="result"></div>
    </form>
</body>
</html>